th a Little Help from My Fwends''''' is the second main album of the \"Fwends\" series by American [[Rock music|rock]] band [[the Flaming Lips]]. It is a track-for-track tribute to [[the Beatles]] album ''[[Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band]]''.<ref name=\"BBC\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-27441301 |title=Flaming Lips to re-record Sgt Pepper with Miley Cyrus |date=May 16, 2014 |accessdate=May 16, 2014 |work=BBC News}}</ref> It was released on October 27, 2014, through [[Warner Bros. Records]].<ref name=\"musictimes\">{{cite web|url=http://www.musictimes.com/articles/6146/20140515/flaming-lips-announce-release-date-sgt-peppers-cover-album-little.htm |title=The Flaming Lips announce release date for 'Sgt. Pepper's' cover album, 'With A Little Help From My Fwends' |date=May 16, 2014 |accessdate=May 16, 2014 |work=Music Times}}</ref> All proceeds from record sales will go to the Bella Foundation, an organization in [[Oklahoma City]] that helps provide veterinary care to pet owners in need.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2014/10/19/356125413/first-listen-the-flaming-lips-with-a-little-help-from-my-fwends|title=First Listen: The Flaming Lips, 'With A Little Help From My Fwends'|date=October 19, 2014|work=NPR.org|accessdate=October 24, 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"RollingStone\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/flaming-lips-sgt-peppers-tribute-album-out-this-fall-20140515 |title=Flaming Lips' 'Sgt. Peppers' Tribute Album Out this Fall |date=May 16, 2014 |accessdate=May 16, 2014 |work=Rolling Stone}}</ref><ref name=\"Pitchfork\">{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/55211-the-flaming-lips-announce-sgt-peppers-lonely-hearts-club-band-tribute-album-release-date/ |title=The Flaming Lips Announce Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band Tribute Album Release Date |date=May 16, 2014 |accessdate=May 16, 2014 |work=Pitchfork}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{tracklist\n| total_length    = 51:24\n| all_writing = [[Lennon\